  "keyFeatures": [
    "Modular design for building custom detection frameworks",
    "Support for object detection, instance segmentation, panoptic segmentation, and semi-supervised detection",
    "100+ pretrained models including Faster R-CNN, Mask R-CNN, DETR, RTMDet, DINO, and Grounding DINO",
    "High-efficiency GPU-accelerated bbox and mask operations",
    "Flexible configuration system based on MMEngine",
    "Rich data augmentation transforms pipeline",
    "Built-in visualization and analysis tools",
    "Support for COCO, LVIS, VOC, OpenImages, and custom datasets"
  ],
